{
  "stem": "10588.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They put us in hermetically sealed cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't count them, but it was packed like sardines, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember a terrible smell because there was-- you know, from the people got sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So all, all the unpleasant things of the body was all in the car.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people were crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, children were crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a horrible journey.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, when we arrived on November 22, 1942, a few people in our car were dead already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What were people talking about?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some were crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were praying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not a normal conversation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody said [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where are they taking us?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When are we going to get off?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They promised us food and things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When are we going to get there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't wait to get there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we were traveling without knowing where we are going at all.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What your parents telling you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember too much conversation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think everybody was very much into themselves and grieving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I do remember-- not so much telling-- but my mother was trying to-- like she usually used to do-- to put her arms around and embrace us all.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's like the saying Yiddish, [YIDDISH], like cuddle up all to the parents and just hoping to stay together.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't have the slightest inclination where we are going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we came, and the time stopped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everything was so fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[GERMAN] quickly, you know, the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I saw some people in, in striped--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived at the train station, the doors swung open.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Nazis were chasing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fast!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Out, out, out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Leave all the packages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't understand why or anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
